{"id":4114,"date":"2025-06-14T14:44:52","date_gmt":"2025-06-14T07:44:52","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=4114"},"modified":"2025-06-14T14:45:20","modified_gmt":"2025-06-14T07:45:20","slug":"bao-lau-tay-da-chet-1-lan","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/bao-lau-tay-da-chet-1-lan\/","title":{"rendered":"Bao l\u00e2u t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft 1 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 da lu\u00f4n kh\u1ecfe \u0111\u1eb9p?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/bao-lau-tay-da-chet-1-lan\/\"><b><i>Bao l\u00e2u t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft 1 l\u1ea7n<\/i><\/b><\/a><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> l\u00e0 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi quan t\u00e2m khi ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da. T\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf l\u1edbp s\u1eebng gi\u00e0, th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da, mang l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da s\u00e1ng m\u1ecbn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n qu\u00e1 \u00edt, da c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u, b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu t\u1ea9y qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u, da d\u1ec5 m\u1ea5t \u0111i l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, tr\u1edf n\u00ean nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng. V\u1eady t\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t n\u00e0o l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng GSC t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u c\u00e1ch t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft khoa h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ec3 da lu\u00f4n kh\u1ecfe \u0111\u1eb9p!<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tay-da-chet-la-gi-tai-sao-da-can-loai-bo-te-bao-chet\"><\/span><b>T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft l\u00e0 g\u00ec? T\u1ea1i sao da c\u1ea7n lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Bao l\u00e2u t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft 1 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft l\u00e0 g\u00ec m\u00e0 l\u1ea1i quan tr\u1ecdng trong quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da? T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf l\u1edbp t\u1ebf b\u00e0o s\u1eebng gi\u00e0 c\u1ed7i tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da. Gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da s\u00e1ng m\u1ecbn, h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. Trung b\u00ecnh, da s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o theo chu k\u1ef3 kho\u1ea3ng 28 ng\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o l\u1edbp t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft c\u0169ng bong ra ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n. Khi t\u00edch t\u1ee5 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u, ch\u00fang c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn da tr\u1edf n\u00ean x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u. G\u00e2y b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng, m\u1ee5n v\u00e0 l\u00e3o h\u00f3a s\u1edbm.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4088\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4088\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4088\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-1.webp\" alt=\"T\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft cho da l\u00e0 sao\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4088\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft cho da l\u00e0 sao<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tay-da-chet-co-tac-dung-gi-vi-sao-can-thuc-hien-dung-cach\"><\/span><b>T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng g\u00ec? V\u00ec sao c\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Bao l\u00e2u t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft 1 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sau b\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0o trong quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da l\u00e0 hai c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi quan t\u00e2m. T\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf l\u1edbp s\u1eebng gi\u00e0 c\u1ed7i, k\u00edch th\u00edch t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o t\u1ebf b\u00e0o m\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00fang th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc skincare sau \u0111\u00f3.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft n\u00ean th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n sau b\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0o? Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n sau b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da (r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t) v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng toner. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t t\u1eeb serum v\u00e0 kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4116\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4116\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4116\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/48-2.webp\" alt=\"T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/48-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/48-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/48-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/48-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4116\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng g\u00ec<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1eafc t\u1ed1: Lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf t\u1ebf b\u00e0o gi\u00e0 c\u1ed7i gi\u00fap da \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u, r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1 h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n, ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba: L\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng h\u01a1n, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf s\u1ef1 t\u00edch t\u1ee5 b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o h\u00f3a: K\u00edch th\u00edch s\u1ea3n sinh collagen, gi\u00fap da s\u0103n ch\u1eafc, gi\u1ea3m n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t: C\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc d\u01b0\u1ee1ng sau s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng khi da s\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"bao-lau-tay-da-chet-1-lan-nen-thuc-hien-may-lan-moi-tuan\"><\/span><b>Bao l\u00e2u t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft 1 l\u1ea7n? N\u00ean th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ea5y l\u1ea7n m\u1ed7i tu\u1ea7n?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc thi\u1ebft y\u1ebfu gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u. D\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 h\u01a1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, &#8220;1 tu\u1ea7n t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft m\u1ea5y l\u1ea7n?&#8221; l\u00e0 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u0103n kho\u0103n. V\u00ec n\u1ebfu th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n qu\u00e1 \u00edt. Da s\u1ebd t\u00edch t\u1ee5 t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft g\u00e2y x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u, b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu t\u1ea9y qu\u00e1 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, da c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, m\u1ea5t \u0111i l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn t\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho t\u1eebng lo\u1ea1i da:<\/span><\/p>\n<p>Bao l\u00e2u t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft 1 l\u1ea7n<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1-da-kho-da-nhay-cam\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">1. Da kh\u00f4, da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da kh\u00f4 ho\u1eb7c nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, ch\u1ec9 n\u00ean t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft <\/span><b>1 l\u1ea7n\/tu\u1ea7n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng. H\u00e3y \u01b0u ti\u00ean s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9 nh\u01b0 <\/span><b>AHA (Acid Lactic, Acid Mandelic)<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> ho\u1eb7c enzyme tr\u00e1i c\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y kh\u00f4 da.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2-da-dau-da-mun\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">2. Da d\u1ea7u, da m\u1ee5n<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0n da d\u1ea7u c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng ti\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn, d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng. V\u00ec v\u1eady, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft <\/span><b>2-3 l\u1ea7n\/tu\u1ea7n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t d\u1ea7u v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n. S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 <\/span><b>BHA (Salicylic Acid)<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u, lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y b\u00e0o m\u00f2n da.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3-da-hon-hop\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">3. Da h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p c\u00f3 v\u00f9ng ch\u1eef T d\u1ea7u nh\u01b0ng hai b\u00ean m\u00e1 l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4, v\u00ec th\u1ebf n\u00ean k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u1ea3 t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 v\u1eadt l\u00fd. T\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng l\u00e0 <\/span><b>2-3 l\u1ea7n\/tu\u1ea7n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">, t\u1eadp trung nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u00e0o v\u00f9ng da d\u1ea7u. Acid Mandelic ho\u1eb7c t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft d\u1ea1ng gel l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u00edch h\u1ee3p cho l\u00e0n da n\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4-da-thuong\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">4. Da th\u01b0\u1eddng<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe, c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng d\u1ea7u &#8211; n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ed1t, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft <\/span><b>2 l\u1ea7n\/tu\u1ea7n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">. C\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a AHA s\u1ebd gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da s\u00e1ng m\u1ecbn. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba l\u00e3o h\u00f3a s\u1edbm.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Duy tr\u00ec t\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p s\u1ebd gi\u00fap da lu\u00f4n s\u1ea1ch kh\u1ecfe. M\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng hay t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u00e3y lu\u00f4n l\u1eafng nghe l\u00e0n da v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh t\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u kh\u00f4 c\u0103ng ho\u1eb7c nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m nh\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"huong-dan-tay-da-chet-dung-cach-de-da-luon-khoe-dep\"><\/span><b>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 da lu\u00f4n kh\u1ecfe \u0111\u1eb9p<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da s\u00e1ng kh\u1ecfe. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sau b\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0o. Hay <\/span><b>bao l\u00e2u t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft 1 l\u1ea7n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Vi\u1ec7c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00fang quy tr\u00ecnh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap da lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba. Kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn cho da t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ho\u1eb7c g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn \u0111ang b\u0103n kho\u0103n 1 tu\u1ea7n t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft m\u1ea5y l\u1ea7n. C\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u ngay c\u00e1ch th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n chu\u1ea9n nh\u1ea5t nh\u00e9:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4117\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4117\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4117\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/48-3.webp\" alt=\"H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 da lu\u00f4n kh\u1ecfe \u0111\u1eb9p\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/48-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/48-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/48-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/48-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4117\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 da lu\u00f4n kh\u1ecfe \u0111\u1eb9p<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"chuan-bi-truoc-khi-tay-da-chet\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Gi\u00e3n n\u1edf l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">: R\u1eeda m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u1ea5m ho\u1eb7c x\u00f4ng h\u01a1i nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng v\u1edbi th\u1ea3o m\u1ed9c. Nh\u01b0 tr\u00e0 xanh, hoa c\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng. T\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>R\u1eeda m\u1eb7t s\u1ea1ch<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">: D\u00f9ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi lo\u1ea1i da \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba. Sau \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ea5m nh\u1eb9 b\u1eb1ng kh\u0103n m\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tien-hanh-tay-te-bao-chet\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sau khi l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4118\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4118\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4118\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/48-4.webp\" alt=\"t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft GSC \" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/48-4.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/48-4-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/48-4-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/48-4-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4118\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft GSC<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><b>Ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">: Da d\u1ea7u, m\u1ee5n n\u00ean d\u00f9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a BHA, da kh\u00f4 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn AHA, ho\u1eb7c t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft t\u1eeb thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0 mu\u1ed1i bi\u1ec3n, enzyme tr\u00e1i c\u00e2y.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n massage nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">: Thoa s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m l\u00ean da v\u00e0 massage theo chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00f2n trong kho\u1ea3ng 30 gi\u00e2y \u2013 1 ph\u00fat. Tr\u00e1nh ch\u00e0 x\u00e1t m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da. <\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>R\u1eeda l\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ea1ch<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">: D\u00f9ng n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e1t r\u1eeda l\u1ea1i m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"duong-da-sau-khi-tay-te-bao-chet\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u01b0\u1ee1ng da sau khi t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sau khi t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft, l\u00e0n da th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m h\u01a1n. V\u00ec v\u1eady c\u1ea7n ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng toner<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">: Gi\u00fap c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 pH v\u00e0 se kh\u00edt l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><b>D\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">: Thoa serum ho\u1eb7c kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><b>B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">: D\u00f9ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u00e0o ban ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh t\u00e1c h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tia UV.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft da m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch t\u1eeb 1 \u0111\u1ebfn 2 l\u1ea7n\/tu\u1ea7n s\u1ebd gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da b\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n s\u00e1ng kho\u1ebb. Tu\u1ef3 v\u00e0o t\u1eebng lo\u1ea1i da, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn t\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u01a1pk nh\u00e9. Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u1edbi kem t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft GSC. S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m an to\u00e0n l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi lo\u1ea1i da.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Bao l\u00e2u t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft 1 l\u1ea7n l\u00e0 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi quan t\u00e2m khi ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da. V\u1eady t\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t n\u00e0o l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng GSC t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u c\u00e1ch t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft khoa h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ec3 da lu\u00f4n kh\u1ecfe \u0111\u1eb9p!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":4119,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4114","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4114","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4114"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4114\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4132,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4114\/revisions\/4132"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4119"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4114"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4114"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4114"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}